# Game-state save fixtures are machine-serialized, pretty-printed JSON dumps of
# the entire board/unit/model state. They are committed so the windowed
# scenarios can load them from a clean checkout, but they are generated data —
# not human-reviewed source. Treat them as binary so they don't render as
# enormous (100k+ line) text diffs, and mark them generated so GitHub collapses
# them in PR review.
*.w40ksave binary linguist-generated=true
